title: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems
description: Bug 19458[Navigator] Copy Project dialog UI problems. The text in the description is displayed in red.
OB: When selecting the project name as 'test', a static text validation error appears on the dialog.
EB: When I uncheck the default location checkbox, the default location should remain in the edit box without being cleared. It should be displayed in black text and include the standard on-the-fly validation small error icon.
